      <h3>Curated with Intention</h3>
      <p>aeladaily was born from a simple idea: everyday objects should bring quiet joy. We travel the world's artisan workshops — from the linen mills of Zhejiang to the weaving studios of Shandong — to find pieces that embody craftsmanship, natural beauty, and timeless design.</p>
      <p>Every product we select is made from <strong>natural materials</strong> — cotton, linen, hemp, wood, beeswax, and ceramic. No plastic, no synthetics. Just honest materials that age beautifully and feel wonderful to touch.</p>

